data.description: Beautiful home that is a true 5 bedroom with a bonus room in sought after Twin Bridges. The kitchen is a dream with huge island, there are THREE ovens, a commercial grade dual fuel gas range that has 2 ovens, then an additional built-in electric oven. Large walk-in pantry, and a nice sized dining area that can accommodate a large table. Excellent floor plan with 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths all on the main level having separate wings of the home. Upstairs is the 5th bedroom, another full bath and a bonus room that could be used as a guest room or another bedroom. Neutral designer colors and all brand new carpet throughout the home. The covered back patio has a wood burning fireplace  & a hot tub for those chilly fall evenings. The secluded cul-de-sac location makes this the perfects setting and the backyard faces east so you can enjoy the outside during our hot summer months due to how the home faces, the yard is shaded.There is a STORM SHELTER in the garage.  Twin Bridges has a large home owners pool and club house with a pond for fishing. Great location that is close shops, grocery & restaurants. This one is priced to sell so don't wait!, schedule your showing now!! Initial contract fell thru due to buyer's inability to obtain funding and was due to no fault of the seller.
